---
---
<section id="inicio" class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-20 overflow-hidden">
    
    <!-- Imagen de Fondo a Pantalla Completa -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img src="/Header.jpg" alt="Fondo ICEVA" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center opacity-70" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
        <!-- Gradiente superpuesto -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-smoke-900/80 via-smoke-900/60 to-smoke-900"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Destellos azules -->
    <div class="flare-bg w-[500px] h-[500px] top-[-100px] left-[-100px] z-0"></div>
    <div class="flare-bg w-[600px] h-[600px] bottom-[-200px] right-[-100px] opacity-70 z-0"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-10">
        <span class="gsap-hero block text-blue-200 tracking-[0.2em] text-sm uppercase mb-4 font-semibold font-sans">Iglesia Cristiana Evangélica</span>
        
        <!-- Degradado de Dorado a Azul en lugar de naranja -->
        <h1 class="gsap-hero text-6xl md:text-8xl font-serif text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
            Vida en <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-200 to-blue-500">Abundancia</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="gsap-hero text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light font-sans">
            Un espacio de fe, esperanza y comunidad. Encuentra propósito, esperanza y una familia real.
            Transformando vidas en Jesús. Bienvenido a tu casa.
        </p>
        <div class="gsap-hero flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4">
            <a href="#horarios" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-white text-smoke-900 rounded-full font-semibold font-sans hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-white/10">
                Nuestros Servicios
            </a>
            <a href="#contacto" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 border border-smoke-700 text-white rounded-full font-semibold font-sans hover:border-blue-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Cómo llegar
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>